messages.messageBody:
Seeking help identifying symbols on my first armor. New to this study
and, a bit overwhelmed. Dou is leather, on the front are three type of
fruit with leafs, connected by pipeing to center, all boardered by a
double circle of what might be oak leaves. If someone could just point
me in right direction, I would be grateful,this armor has a feeling or
presence, that my wife even can sense. I feel that it would be proper
to find out more about who this is. With Thanks,Bud.
